{"tid":1942110,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：泛民及大部分香港人令我丟失生計，現在各位見到惡果。2019年的香港法權剝奪、2020年的瘟疫奪權只是前菜。","createTime":"2020-03-25T00:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T11:01:44.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ed3cc10e479ea2ba1fc07b12ea54e651681fc10a","tid":1942110,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:38:17.000Z","msg":"陳雲：我是預知未來的人。你可以叫我做先知，我只會悲傷，我不會反對。我是世界上最早提出decoupling with China（脫離中國）計劃的人，我的香港修憲計劃在2016年被泛民及大部分香港人摧毀。之後他們對我鋪天蓋地的攻擊和污衊，令我丟失生計。<br />\n現在各位見到惡果，2019年的香港法權剝奪，只是共產黨的香檳酒。2020年的瘟疫奪權，是第一道前菜。"},{"pid":"c739cea027f8608a7a8dd6741417f475a20574ee","tid":1942110,"uid":53105,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:45:15.000Z","msg":"點解無預見自己失敗"},{"pid":"871ce461f2f898456a86e83118363a2e6be01637","tid":1942110,"uid":184726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:09:41.000Z","msg":"如果冇陳雲個名仲以為係邊個建制奶共狗寫嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f5366a281afb6833f443a5f25649d7fbd4f17e","tid":1942110,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"痴線佬"},{"pid":"fbb699497e03b7a437f7032577833fa68dedd65a","tid":1942110,"uid":69806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:31:36.000Z","msg":"重點係令我丟失生計"},{"pid":"592d86e7bcaf3edc42215c1aefd1bff9fca78c47","tid":1942110,"uid":135408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"丟失生計先係重點<br />\n廢老就該石沉大海 好好養老"},{"pid":"1c7fdbd8382ff60c4f94ba4396139cfedaae1ab1","tid":1942110,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:49:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>國師又中！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"990f980076f0ce937ba364fa394b3c97749dc141","tid":1942110,"uid":185656,"like":15,"disli